main event: On October 26, 1966, two witnesses observed a UFO for 40 minutes in Massillon, Ohio.
interesting points: The object was observed moving north-south,The observation lasted for 40 minutes,The witnesses reported a distinct rushing sound made by the object,The conclusion reached by the project was insufficient data for evaluation,There was no photograph available but there was mention of a letter from Major Hector Quintanilla regarding the sighting.
witness description: two witnesses present during the observation
